    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system overhaul. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in. While minor aesthetic imperfections exist, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and oil analysis\u2014confirm a healthy, high-revving powerplant ready for the enthusiast driver.",
